{"tid":2022373,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"基亞連尼：和沙利談話後必須洗澡 否則會一身煙味","createTime":"2020-05-18T09:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T10:22:44.000Z","uid":225130,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9a9ced5abe7077bf3b97d5e7ba81c109c2de64","tid":2022373,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:42:51.000Z","msg":"基亞連尼：和沙利談話後必須洗澡 否則會一身煙味<br />\n2020年05月18日17:24<br />\n<br />\n  祖記後衛基亞連尼透露，主教練沙利愛抽菸，這讓很多球員對他避而不及。<br />\n<br />\n  61歲的沙利據說一天要抽60根菸，基亞連尼在自傳中稱，祖記球員在和沙利談話之後，都必須去洗澡，否則會被熏得一身煙味。「有一件事情，沒有人能夠改變他，那就是對抽菸的依賴。」<br />\n<br />\n  「你去到他的辦公室里和他談話，之後你只能去洗澡，否則的話，我們會聞起來一身煙味。」<br />\n<br />\n  「他一直在尋求完美，比如在對方半場里，要百分之百的控球權，這當然是一種空想，但也許這種追求，讓他從底層一路打上來，達到了現在的位置。」"},{"pid":"3d09916384166603d13a744b7b8a3aad16d67011","tid":2022373,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/05/17/15/28497692-0-image-m-84_1589726532200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F05%2F17%2F15%2F28497692-0-image-m-84_1589726532200.jpg&h=a1c686ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/05/17/15/28497388-0-image-a-78_1589726426607.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F05%2F17%2F15%2F28497388-0-image-a-78_1589726426607.jpg&h=e58d6394&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"220c74d59274482c46dd95b0ef58a4bca1dad9f9","tid":2022373,"uid":277389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:45:49.000Z","msg":"（長文）（置頂）(戰術）金鐘野餐攻略 沙盤推演<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2018117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2018117</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nu6c2QF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnu6c2QF.jpg&h=61dc0e61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b3f790f7c128d746dd41edd9e7fb0093d6c15c1","tid":2022373,"uid":13732,"like":1,"